	‚ÄúI&#039;m supposed to be, yeah. Why do you ask?‚Äù
	‚ÄúWell, you said that business was slow, I figured you might want to show me the sights. Your parents are out of town, right? If you close up for a few hours, they&#039;ll never find out.‚Äù
